description: Remember Jamie from Crossin' the Line and Crossin' the Line 2? That nervous hot guy that broke down and gave it all to Big Jake like he might have fallen in love? Well, somewhere in between Crossin' the Line and Crossin' the Line 2 I paired him up with Pratt from Another Tour of Duty and these two had a little fun but didn't finish the deed. Pratt was basically prying Jamie out of his shell and it wasn't an easy task, but the build-up to that moment is what makes this week's War Chest Update so special. Take a look!
title: Jamie & Pratt
